## Title: LibCodex-1.0-Vignettes
## Notes: Bundled seed data for LibCodex-1.0 / Vignettes (MoP Classic flavor). LoadOnDemand: LibCodex-1.0 auto-loads this on first :Get() miss against the Vignettes module. Per-module split keeps the core lib's bytecode pool tiny and lets consumers pay only for modules they query.
